lking on its newly grown legs, it always  swims around in water."},{"version":"silver","text":"The direction of its belly spiral differs by area. The equator is thought to have an effect on this."},{"version":"crystal","text":"The swirl on its belly is its insides showing through the skin. It looks clearer after it eats."},{"version":"ruby","text":"POLIWAG has a very thin skin. It is possible to see the POK\u00e9MON\u2019s spiral innards right through the skin. Despite its thinness, however, the skin is also very flexible. Even sharp fangs bounce right off it."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"POLIWAG has a very thin skin. It is possible to see the POK\u00e9MON\u2019s spiral innards right through the skin. Despite its thinness, however, the skin is also very flexible. Even sharp fangs bounce right off it."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It is possible to see this POK\u00e9MON\u2019s spiral innards right through its thin skin. However, the skin is also very flexible. Even sharp fangs bounce right off it."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its slick black skin is thin and damp. A part of its internal organs can be seen through the skin as a spiral pattern."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Its newly grown legs prevent it from walking well. It appears to prefer swimming over walking."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its skin is so thin, its internal organs are visible. It has trouble walking on its newly grown feet."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its skin is so thin, its internal organs are visible. It has trouble walking on its newly grown feet."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its skin is so thin, its internal organs are visible. It has trouble walking on its newly grown feet."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Because it is inept at walking on its newly grown legs, it always  swims around in water."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"The direction of its belly spiral differs by area. The equator is thought to have an effect on this."},{"version":"black","text":"Its skin is so thin, 